      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1605</offset>
        <text>Our study demonstrates that bacterioplankton RQ is not only a practical aspect of BR determination, but also a major ecosystem state variable that provides unique information about aquatic ecosystem functioning.
</text>
      </sentence>
